Package com.epam.finaltask.dao

Provides interfaces to create and use DAOs and create connection manager.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AccountDao
    Interface that contains methods specific to DAO that works with accounts.
    ConnectionManagerFactory
    Factory which creates AbstractConnectionManager subclass instances.
    Dao<T extends Entity>
    Interface that provides basic DAO methods.
    DaoFactory
    Factory interface that is used to creates DAOs.
    MessageDao
    Interface that contains methods specific to DAO that works with messages.
    TopicDao
    Interface that contains methods specific to DAO that works with topics.
